in multiple locations., Itâ€™s like having a superhero for your website that never sleeps.</p>\n</div>\r\n    <div class=\"mt-xs\">\r\n        <div data-layout=\"button\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/updraftplus/pricing/?utm_source=blog&#038;utm_medium=cta-button&#038;utm_campaign=it-theme&#038;utm_content=explore-updraftplus-premium\" \r\n        class=\"c-btn-md  sm:c-btn-rg  bg-orange  inline-flex  my-4xs  hover:bg-main  focus:bg-main\"\r\n    >\r\n        Explore UpdraftPlus Premium    </a>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</div>\r\n<!-- cta -->\n\n<h2>Whoâ€™s using these themes? Real-world examples</h2>\n<p>If youâ€™re wondering how these themes look in action, hereâ€™s a quick peek at tech and IT websites that rely on these WordPress themes to power their online presence. Seeing them can help you understand which theme might suit your site best.</p>\n\n<h3>1. Code Fryx â€“ Built with Blocksy</h3>\n\n<!-- image -->\r\n<figure data-layout=\"image\" class=\"overflow-hidden  rounded-md\" data-alt=\"Screenshot of Codefryx homepage\">\r\n    <img decoding=\"async\"\r\n                class=\"bg-main-1/3  border  border-main-1/10\"\r\n                loading=\"lazy\"\r\n        alt=\"Screenshot of Codefryx homepage\"\r\n        width=\"1428\"\r\n        height=\"896\"\r\n        src=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-640x402.webp\"\r\n        srcset=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-640x402.webp 640w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-1024x643.webp 1024w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-300x188.webp 300w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-1280x803.webp 1280w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-768x482.webp 768w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx-600x376.webp 600w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/codefryx.webp 1428w\"\r\n        sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\r\n    >\r\n    </figure>\r\n<!-- image -->\n\n<p><a href=\"https://codefryx.de\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\" rel=\"nofollow\">Code Fryx</a> is a tech education provider offering courses and camps for children and young people to learn essential tech skills. Their website utilizes the Blocksy theme to create a modern, responsive design that enhances user engagement through intuitive navigation and consistent calls to action.</p>\n\n<h3>2. WP101 â€“ Built with GeneratePress</h3>\n\n<!-- image -->\r\n<figure data-layout=\"image\" class=\"overflow-hidden  rounded-md\" data-alt=\"Screenshot of WP101 homepage\">\r\n    <img decoding=\"async\"\r\n                class=\"bg-main-1/3  border  border-main-1/10\"\r\n                loading=\"lazy\"\r\n        alt=\"Screenshot of WP101 homepage\"\r\n        width=\"1428\"\r\n        height=\"896\"\r\n        src=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-640x402.webp\"\r\n        srcset=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-640x402.webp 640w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-1024x643.webp 1024w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-300x188.webp 300w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-1280x803.webp 1280w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-768x482.webp 768w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101-600x376.webp 600w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/WP101.webp 1428w\"\r\n        sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\r\n    >\r\n    </figure>\r\n<!-- image -->\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wp101.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\" rel=\"nofollow\">WP101</a> is a popular platform offering professional WordPress video tutorials. The site leverages the GeneratePress theme for its clean layout and fast performance.</p>\n\n<h3>3. Wappalyzer â€“ Built with Neve</h3>\n\n<!-- image -->\r\n<figure data-layout=\"image\" class=\"overflow-hidden  rounded-md\" data-alt=\"Screenshot of Wappalyzer homepage\">\r\n    <img decoding=\"async\"\r\n                class=\"bg-main-1/3  border  border-main-1/10\"\r\n                loading=\"lazy\"\r\n        alt=\"Screenshot of Wappalyzer homepage\"\r\n        width=\"1428\"\r\n        height=\"896\"\r\n        src=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-640x402.webp\"\r\n        srcset=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-640x402.webp 640w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-1024x643.webp 1024w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-300x188.webp 300w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-1280x803.webp 1280w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-768x482.webp 768w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer-600x376.webp 600w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/wappalyzer.webp 1428w\"\r\n        sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\r\n    >\r\n    </figure>\r\n<!-- image -->\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.wappalyzer.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wappalyzer</a> is a technology profiler tool that identifies technologies used on websites. Their platform utilizes the Neve theme for its fast and customizable design.</p>\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>Choosing the right theme for your IT website can make or break how clients perceive your brand. The right one blends speed, trust, and professionalism, while leaving room to grow with your business.</p>\n<p>I personally found Astra to be incredibly versatile for almost any IT project, Kadence makes editing a breeze with minimal setup, and Exponent stands out when you want a premium feel.</p>\n<p>One tip from real-world testing: always <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/blog/how-to-backup-a-wordpress-site/\">back up your site</a> before testing themes. Youâ€™ll save yourself headaches later, and your siteâ€™s professionalism will stay intact no matter what.</p>\n\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\n\n<!-- accordion -->\n<div data-layout=\"accordion\" class=\"c-accordion  border-t  border-main-1/10\">\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            What are the best IT WordPress themes for startups?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>The best IT WordPress themes for startups are lightweight, fast, and easy to customize. Themes like Astra, Kadence, and SaaS Software Technology are excellent choices because they provide professional layouts, responsive design, and flexible customization, making them perfect for SaaS platforms, IT consultancies, or small tech businesses.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            What makes a theme good for IT or tech websites?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>Themes built for IT companies focus on speed, SEO, modern layouts, and plugin compatibility. They should support integrations like Elementor, WooCommerce, and <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/all-in-one-security/\">security plugins</a> easily.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            Should I choose a free or premium theme?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>If youâ€™re just starting, free versions of Astra, Neve, or Kadence are excellent. For established IT businesses, premium themes like Exponent provide stronger branding tools and flexibility.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            How easy is it to customize these IT WordPress themes?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>Most themes on this list are very easy to use. Themes like Astra, Neve, and Kadence are beginner-friendly, while slightly more advanced themes like Exponent and OceanWP have a small learning curve but offer extensive customization options. You can modify layouts, colors, typography, and even page structures without touching code.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            Can I integrate e-commerce features with these IT WordPress themes?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>Yes. Themes like OceanWP, Bizora, and Cyberdom are compatible with WooCommerce, allowing IT companies to sell digital products, software subscriptions, or services directly from their WordPress site.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            How do I keep my IT WordPress site secure?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>Regular updates and reliable backups are essential. I recommend using a security plugin like <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/all-in-one-security/\">All-In-One Security (AIOS)</a> to protect your site from threats and UpdraftPlus to <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/updraftplus/features/schedule-wordpress-backup-at-set-times/\">automate backups</a> and store them safely offsite &#8211; giving you full peace of mind</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n        <details class=\"border-b  border-main-1/10  -mt-1  open:text-main-1\">   \n        <summary class=\"reset  cursor-pointer  font-800  leading-none   py-xs  pr-md  text-h6\">\n            Are these themes compatible with Elementor?        </summary>\n        <div class=\"text-main/70  mb-2xs\">\n            <p>Yes, almost all listed themes are Elementor-compatible, and several also work with Bricks or Gutenberg.</p>\n        </div>\n    </details>\n    </div>\n<!-- accordion -->\n\n\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Author -->\n                <div class=\"mt-rg\">\n                    <h3 class=\"mb-xs\">About the author</h3>\n                    <div class=\"col-end-s5  flex\">\n                        <div>\n                            <div class=\"block  bg-white  border-3  border-orange  mr-xs  overflow-hidden  rounded-full  relative  size-[70px]\">\n                                <figure class=\"block  absolute  inset-[3px]  rounded-full  overflow-hidden\">\n                                                                        <img decoding=\"async\"\n                                        class=\"absolute  inset-0  m-auto  object-cover  h-full  w-full\"\n                                        loading=\"lazy\" \n                                        alt=\"\"\n                                        width=\"109\"\n                                        height=\"150\"\n                                        src=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Elvira-Mishra-217x300.jpg\"\n                                    >\n                                                                    </figure>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h4 class=\"block  text-rg  my-4xs  font-800\">Elvira Mishra</h4>\n                            <p class