ses-1024x480.png\"\n                        srcset=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-1024x480.png 1024w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-1440x675.png 1440w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-300x141.png 300w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-1280x600.png 1280w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-640x300.png 640w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-768x360.png 768w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-1680x788.png 1680w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-1920x900.png 1920w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases-600x281.png 600w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WPO-releases.png 2560w\"\n                        sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n                    >\n                </figure>\n                                        <h3 class=\"text-h5  leading-xs  -line-clamp-4  mt-sm  mb-2xs\">\n                <a href=\"https://teamupdraft.com/blog/wp-optimize-release-v4-2-3/\" class=\"group  after:absolute  after:inset-0  after:h-full  z-10\">\n                    WP-Optimize release v4.2.3: Power up your site&#8217;s performance with key fixes and tweaks                    <i class=\"absolute  bottom-xs  right-xs  text-h3  text-orange  group-focus:-rotate-45  group-hover:-rotate-45  group-focus:transition-all  group-hover:transition-all  z-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path d=\"M686-450H190q-13 0-21.5-8.5T160-480q0-13 8.5-21.5T190-510h496L459-737q-9-9-9-21t9-21q9-9 21-9t21 9l278 278q5 5 7 10t2 11q0 6-2 11t-7 10L501-181q-9 9-21 9t-21-9q-9-9-9-21t9-21l227-227Z\"/></svg>                    </i>\n                </a>\n            </h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm  md:text-md  sr-only  sm:not-sr-only  sm:line-clamp-2  md:line-clamp-3  text-main/70  mb-4xs\">Learn whatâ€™s new in WP-Optimize 4.2.3, including caching and image fixes.</p>\n            <time class=\"absolute  bottom-sm  text-xs  md:text-sm  font-800\" datetime=\"2025-07-25\">25 Jul 2025</time>\n        </div>\n    </article>\n</li><li class=\"reset  flex  items-stretch\">        \n    <article class=\"block  h-full  w-full\">\n        <div class=\"reset  block  group  border  border-l-0  border-main-1/20  h-full  rounded-r-lg  p-sm  pb-lg  lg:pb-rg  pl-0  xl:pr-xs  relative  w-full  shadow-[4px_4px_8px_hsla(var(--color-main),.03)]\">\n                                            <figure class=\"block  relative  bg-main-1/3  pb-[70%]  overflow-hidden  -mr-sm  -mt-sm  xl:-mr-xs  rounded-tr-lg\">\n                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n                        class=\"object-cover  absolute  inset-0  m-auto  w-full  h-full\" \n                        alt=\"\"\n                        width=\"2560\"\n                        height=\"1200\"\n                        src=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1024x480.png\"\n                        srcset=\"https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1024x480.png 1024w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1440x675.png 1440w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-300x141.png 300w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1280x600.png 1280w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-640x300.png 640w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-768x360.png 768w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1680x788.png 1680w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcements-1920x900.png 1920w, https://teamupdraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/TU-announcement